reviews.review_text:
What a run! :) The SBD's of this run are crisp, but I prefer the AUD's - more bass.

These three shows were a delight all the way around.  The band was in good spirits, and the weather/vibe were perfect.

Energy levels and 'X-Factor' were up/present all three nights.  This night is pretty straightforward, but all songs are well played.  (The next night has the best Playin' of the 90's easily - it's a 20+ minute weirdness tour de force.)
